
visible(2)                 silmul_efun                 visible(2)

名称
     visible() - 检查某个物件是否可见(是否隐藏)

语法
     varargs int visible( object detectee, object detector )

描述
     Returns:     1 if detector may be allowed to know  that  the
     detectee exists
                  0 if  detector  may  not  penetrate  detectee's
     invisibility.

作者
     Pallando
     wade@future 4/8/1996 翻译

MudOS Release 0.9         Last change:                   3-19-93

